# Delay sweep: keep constant CPS while sweeping server response delay.
# Useful to find the delay threshold where errors start appearing.
#
# Usage:
#   tools/events-schedule.sh tools/events-schedule-examples/delay-sweep.driver

Timeline(s)   cps:myFlow   vault:RESPONSE_DELAY_MS   snapshot
0             1000         0                         start
30            -            50                        -
60            -            100                       -
90            -            200                       -
120           -            500                       -
150           -            1000                      -
180           -            2000                      -
210           0            0                         end
